                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 14.402,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 86350,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in United States against Clarke will be announced by Mr. Justice Rehnquist along with Rummel against Estelle."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 14.402,
                        "stop": 140.922,
